Title: Coyotes
Writer: Christophe Beaujean, Axel du Bus de Warnaffe, Vincent Lavachery
Actors: Olivia Castanho, Louka Minnella, Andria Kozica
Plot: A scout patrol stumbles upon diamonds during a camp. Torn between give them back, sharing them, or keeping them, each member questions his own morality. Meanwhile, there is a danger for the wasps: those who lost them are willing to do anything to find them.
